%% Figure 3.5 — State diagram: Question approval lifecycle.
%% QForge — Question lifecycle state diagram (Chapter 3, §3.1.3).
%% Reconciled against questions.status enum (pending|approved|rejected) and the
%% source-dependent entry points in PLAN.md / MILESTONES.md:
%%  - extracted candidates and manual drafts enter as `pending`;
%%  - AI top-up questions are stored directly as `approved` (else the generator's
%%    CandidateFilter, which selects status=approved only, could never use them);
%%  - only `approved` questions are eligible for paper generation.
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> pending : extracted / manual create
    [*] --> approved : AI top-up (source = ai)
    pending --> approved : admin approves
    pending --> rejected : admin rejects
    approved --> [*] : deleted / re-extracted
    rejected --> [*] : discarded

    note right of approved
        Only approved questions are
        selectable by the generator.
    end note
